item.title: Adelaide CS Community Project
item.description: When I first knew Garbage Collection Mechanism in Java, I felt it was quite appealing to me, especially for a C++ programmer, because I do not need to worry about the memory leak anymore; therefore I started learning Java in April 2022. On December 22, 2022, I started my Java full-stack project. This post will keep track of my progress of developing this project.
